info.author: Alexandre Vicenzi
info.description:
Python library for Telize JSON IP and GeoIP REST API.

For examples visit our GitHub page.

About Telize:

Telize offers a REST API allowing to get a visitor IP address and to query location information from any IP address.

There is no rate limit of any sort at the moment, and the service is free for everyone to use.

Visit http://www.telize.com/
